rename it and rename its name in docker-compose.yml

the content should be like that:

DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://pg-username:pg-password@postgres:5432/pg-database_name
POSTGRES_USER=pg-username
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=pg-password
POSTGRES_DB=pg-database_name
JWT_SECRET_KEY=precalculated key: secrets.token_hex(32 / 64)